{"tid":2479151,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"最近有兩位在囚手足生日","createTime":"2021-04-07T15:10:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T15:26:30.000Z","uid":280525,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9feeb4b6093cb1f5682393180d8197425a0e3fc4","tid":2479151,"uid":280525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T15:10:42.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"large\"><strong>1.【白羊座手足生日祝福】</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n為4月生日嘅手足徵生日書信!!!<br />\n<br />\n如你有意成為寫信師，抬頭可寫比 <br />\n白羊座仔仔，並於2021年<span class=\"orange\">4月12日或之前</span>，將信件以<span class=\"orange\">親身/郵寄方式交往（天水圍連線）辦事處</span>代為處理。<br />\n<br />\nP.S由於懲教署對於卡片數量有所管制，建議以信件方式寄予手足<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/tswconnection/2342\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftswconnection%2F2342&d=kuRIuFMgKSvsW5TefiiiYYeNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=33c2d082\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/tswconnection/2342</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CNXZohcjLOx/?igshid=2j29iu9gzf4h\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCNXZohcjLOx%2F%3Figshid%3D2j29iu9gzf4h&d=kuRIuFMgKSvsW5TefiiiYYeNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=71073026\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCNXZohcjLOx%2F%3Figshid%3D2j29iu9gzf4h&h=ef3015d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CNXZohcjLOx/?igshid=2j29iu9gzf4h</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><strong>2.【為鄭手足送上生日祝福】</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n鄭手足已還押逾1個月，今個月尾她將在獄中渡過生日。石牆花在此呼籲有心人為她來寫生日信，歡迎大家寄生日信件給這位手足，將溫暖送到她的手中🙏🏻<br />\n<br />\n為免信件延誤，請在<span class=\"orange\">4月16日前把信件寄至石牆花。<br />\n<br />\n地址：九龍荔枝角青山道485號九龍廣場11樓01室<br />\n</span><br />\n***由於懲教署對卡類（生日卡/節日卡等）有數量限制，敬請大家不要寄生日卡過來，石牆花只會轉寄生日信，感謝！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_mailbox/716\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_mailbox%2F716&d=kuRIuFMgKSvsW5TefiiiYYeNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=f41a997a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_mailbox/716</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CNR5v0lAPi-/?igshid=13yhjcejc5d4s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCNR5v0lAPi-%2F%3Figshid%3D13yhjcejc5d4s&d=kuRIuFMgKSvsW5TefiiiYYeNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=51c33b2c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCNR5v0lAPi-%2F%3Figshid%3D13yhjcejc5d4s&h=d941c974\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CNR5v0lAPi-/?igshid=13yhjcejc5d4s</a>"},{"pid":"33a1d52971f7d688e808b8ccc1f14b54e8739c3a","tid":2479151,"uid":142002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T15:11:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a933a820bbf76fa89390e4800d424dc08263b612","tid":2479151,"uid":280525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T15:12:00.000Z","msg":"寄畀1. 白羊座手足<br />\n<br />\n🔻 以下為天水連線聯絡方法🔻<br />\n<br />\n官方頻道：@tswconnection<br />\n<br />\n伍健偉<br />\n@tswconnection_LuciferKng<br />\n林    進<br />\n@tswconnection_lamchun<br />\n侯文健<br />\n@tswconnection_haumankin<br />\n關俊笙<br />\n@tswconnection_leonkwan <br />\n<br />\n電話聯絡： <br />\n伍健偉：56808500<br />\n林    進：97467106<br />\n侯文健：67601781<br />\n關俊笙：57148371 <br />\n天水連線：96531637<br />\n<br />\n辦事處地址<br />\n關俊笙：天水圍天恩邨恩福樓地下5號<br />\n林    進：天水圍天瑞邨瑞財樓地下2號<br />\n伍健偉：天水圍嘉湖 + woo 一期251室<br />\n侯文健：天水圍新北江商場1/F B6號舖"},{"pid":"4bfc4d4693578c389515bc1e1a266d4b96d7d6c1","tid":2479151,"uid":142002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T15:12:06.000Z","msg":"生日快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fb8543197d142181edfc3ae86d30c332536a45d","tid":2479151,"uid":280525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid